Interface StopwatchStateMachine

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultStopwatchStateMachine

    public interface StopwatchStateMachine
extends StopwatchUIListener, OnTickListener, StopwatchUIUpdateSource
    The state machine for the state-based dynamic model of the stopwatch. This interface is part of the State pattern.
